[url=https://www.nexusmods.com/kingdomcomedeliverance2/mods/1023][img]https://img.shields.io/badge/Mod-Helmet–Off%20Dialog%20[KCD1]-bf4848?style=flat-square–=nexusmods[/img][/url] [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/kingdomcomedeliverance2/mods/1023][img]https://img.shields.io/badge/Mod-Helmet–Off%20Dialog%20[KCD2]-bf4848?style=flat-square–=nexusmods[/img][/url] [url=https://github.com/rdok/kcd2_helmet_off_dialog][img]https://img.shields.io/badge/Open-Source-2ea44f?style=flat-square&logo=github[/img][/url]

This mod automatically unequips your helmet and coif when starting a conversation with an NPC, then re-equips them when the dialog ends. It’s still in beta, so it’s not perfect yet. For a fully polished version, use Nexus Mods’ watch feature to track this mod and check back later.

