[size=4]Things to Know[/size]
[list]
[*] [b]Charisma Impact[/b]: Unequipping the helmet or coif during dialogue might lower charisma, as these items contribute to that stat. I don’t plan to address this, as high charisma is achievable without them, and it’s an acceptable trade-off for the mod’s functionality.
[*] [b]Not All Helmets[/b]: I play slowly (still on the first map after a restart), so some helmets might not work with the mod. If you find one that doesn’t, let me know.
[*] [b]Non-Helmet Items[/b]: Gear like hats remains unaffected by this mod.
[/list]

[size=4]Planned Features[/size]

I’m considering an alternative version to randomly un-equip the helmet—e.g., off for one dialogue, on for the next. Feedback welcome.

